---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="How We Work - intelio">
<main>
  <!-- HERO SECTION (Dark background) -->
  <section class="py-16 sm:py-20 md:py-24 bg-black text-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl font-normal mb-4 sm:mb-6">How We Work</h1>
      <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-gray-400 mb-6 sm:mb-8">Clear engagement models. No ambiguity. No surprises.</p>
      <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
        intelio installs systems that businesses rely on. How those systems are supported depends on how much execution you want to own.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SECTION 1: Identify + Build + Maintain (Light background) -->
  <section class="py-16 sm:py-20 md:py-24 bg-white text-black">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-normal mb-3 sm:mb-4">Identify + Build + Maintain</h2>
      <p class="text-base sm:text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-6 sm:mb-8">For organizations that want strong systems and internal ownership.</p>
      
      <div class="space-y-6 sm:space-y-8 mb-8 sm:mb-12">
        <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
          We identify where time, money, and momentum are leaking — then design and build the systems that fix it.
        </p>
        <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
          Once live, we maintain those systems so they remain reliable, secure, and effective as the business evolves.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 sm:gap-12 mb-8 sm:mb-12">
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">What this includes</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-700">
              <span class="text-gray-400 mt-1">•</span>
              <span>Business and system assessment</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-700">
              <span class="text-gray-400 mt-1">•</span>
              <span>Architecture and system design</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-700">
              <span class="text-gray-400 mt-1">•</span>
              <span>Implementation and integration</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-700">
              <span class="text-gray-400 mt-1">•</span>
              <span>Documentation and training</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-700">
              <span class="text-gray-400 mt-1">•</span>
              <span>Ongoing maintenance, updates, and support</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">How it works</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-700">
              <span class="text-gray-400 mt-1">•</span>
              <span>You operate the systems day-to-day</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-700">
              <span class="text-gray-400 mt-1">•</span>
              <span>We ensure they stay healthy and aligned</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-700">
              <span class="text-gray-400 mt-1">•</span>
              <span>Improvements are handled without disruption</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-500 italic">Best for: Teams that want control without technical burden.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SECTION 2: Identify + Build + Operate (Dark background) -->
  <section class="py-16 sm:py-20 md:py-24 bg-black text-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-normal mb-3 sm:mb-4">Identify + Build + Operate</h2>
      <p class="text-base sm:text-lg font-semibold text-gray-300 mb-6 sm:mb-8">For organizations that want execution off their plate.</p>
      
      <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-8 sm:mb-12">
        We identify and build the same systems — then we run them with you or for you, inside clearly defined guardrails.
      </p>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 sm:gap-12 mb-8 sm:mb-12">
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">What this includes</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-300">
              <span class="text-gray-500 mt-1">•</span>
              <span>Everything in Build + Maintain</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-300">
              <span class="text-gray-500 mt-1">•</span>
              <span>Ongoing system operation</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-300">
              <span class="text-gray-500 mt-1">•</span>
              <span>Workflow execution and monitoring</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-300">
              <span class="text-gray-500 mt-1">•</span>
              <span>Exception handling and optimization</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-300">
              <span class="text-gray-500 mt-1">•</span>
              <span>Regular performance review</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">How it works</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-300">
              <span class="text-gray-500 mt-1">•</span>
              <span>You set direction and priorities</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-300">
              <span class="text-gray-500 mt-1">•</span>
              <span>We execute inside the system</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-300">
              <span class="text-gray-500 mt-1">•</span>
              <span>Visibility and reporting are built in</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-500 italic">Best for: Founder-led, growth-stage, or lean teams that need leverage without adding headcount.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SECTION 3: Select Custom & Advanced Builds (Light background) -->
  <section class="py-16 sm:py-20 md:py-24 bg-white text-black">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-normal mb-3 sm:mb-4">Select Custom & Advanced Builds</h2>
      <p class="text-base sm:text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-6 sm:mb-8">For complex or non-standard environments.</p>
      
      <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-8 sm:mb-12">
        In select cases, intelio undertakes advanced system design or AI-enabled projects where standard configurations are insufficient.
      </p>

      <div class="mb-8 sm:mb-12">
        <h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">These engagements are:</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-700">
            <span class="text-gray-400 mt-1">•</span>
            <span>Selective</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-700">
            <span class="text-gray-400 mt-1">•</span>
            <span>Independently scoped</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-700">
            <span class="text-gray-400 mt-1">•</span>
            <span>Reserved for organizations with operational readiness</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-500 italic">Best for: Businesses operating at scale where standard systems break down.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SECTION 4: Technology Stack (Dark background) -->
  <section class="py-16 sm:py-20 md:py-24 bg-black text-white">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-normal mb-3 sm:mb-4 text-center">The Operating Systems Behind Scalable Businesses</h2>
      <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-gray-400 text-center mb-12 sm:mb-16">
        intelio standardizes on proven platforms across CRM, automation, AI, data, and operations — configured by industry, not reinvented per client.
      </p>

      <!-- SUB-SECTION 4A: Enterprise Foundations -->
      <div class="mb-16 sm:mb-20">
        <h3 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-8 sm:mb-12">Enterprise Foundations</h3>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 sm:gap-8 mb-8">
          <div class="bg-black/30 border border-white/10 p-6 sm:p-8 rounded-xl">
            <h4 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">Microsoft</h4>
            <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-400">Identity, security, automation, data, AI infrastructure.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-black/30 border border-white/10 p-6 sm:p-8 rounded-xl">
            <h4 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">Google</h4>
            <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-400">Workspace, analytics, search, and operational visibility.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-500 italic text-center">These platforms form the foundation — not experiments.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- SUB-SECTION 4B: Intelio Operating Layers (Light background) -->
      <div class="bg-white/5 rounded-2xl p-6 sm:p-8 md:p-12 mb-12 sm:mb-16">
        <h3 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-8 sm:mb-12">Intelio Operating Layers</h3>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6 sm:gap-8">
          <div class="bg-black/30 border border-white/10 p-6 rounded-xl">
            <h4 class="text-base sm:text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-4">Customer & Revenue Operations</h4>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-400">
              <li>• CRM</li>
              <li>• Lead routing</li>
              <li>• Scheduling</li>
              <li>• Billing and payments</li>
              <li>• Review and reputation systems</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-black/30 border border-white/10 p-6 rounded-xl">
            <h4 class="text-base sm:text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-4">Automation & Workflow</h4>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-400">
              <li>• Event-driven workflows</li>
              <li>• Cross-system orchestration</li>
              <li>• Notifications and escalations</li>
              <li>• Compliance and audit logging</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-black/30 border border-white/10 p-6 rounded-xl">
            <h4 class="text-base sm:text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-4">Intelligence & AI</h4>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-400">
              <li>• AI assistants for admin and ops</li>
              <li>• Document processing</li>
              <li>• Forecasting and analysis</li>
              <li>• Embedded decision support</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-black/30 border border-white/10 p-6 rounded-xl">
            <h4 class="text-base sm:text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-4">Finance & Control</h4>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-400">
              <li>• Bookkeeping systems</li>
              <li>• Job costing</li>
              <li>• Margin visibility</li>
              <li>• Cash flow tracking</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- SUB-SECTION 4C: Configured, Not Custom (Dark background) -->
      <div class="mb-12 sm:mb-16">
        <h3 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-6 sm:mb-8">Configured, Not Custom</h3>
        <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
          intelio configures proven systems to your business.
        </p>
        <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mt-4">
          We do not reinvent tools or build fragile one-off stacks. Custom development is reserved for select platform extensions and advanced projects.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- SUB-SECTION 4D: Special Projects (Light background) -->
      <div class="bg-white/5 rounded-2xl p-6 sm:p-8 md:p-12">
        <h3 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-6 sm:mb-8">Special Projects (Selective)</h3>
        <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
          Occasionally, intelio takes on complex system or AI projects for organizations operating at scale.
        </p>
        <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mt-4">
          These engagements are selective and separate from the core platform.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA SECTION (Dark background) -->
  <section class="py-16 sm:py-20 md:py-24 bg-black text-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 text-center">
      <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 bg-white text-black text-base sm:text-lg font-medium rounded-full hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors min-h-[56px]">
        Work with Intelio
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>
</Layout>

